                <p class="body-content">(j) Other personal data prescribed by law as specific and requiring necessary security measures.</p>
                <p class="body-content">Please see details of our Privacy Policy here.</p>
                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">2.5. Protection of personal data</p>
