                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">3.2. E-News will request the User's consent before using the User's personal data for any purpose other than the purposes set out in Article 3.1 above, at the time of collecting the User's personal data or before commencing the relevant processing or as otherwise required or permitted by applicable law.</p>
                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">4. Security of User Personal Data</p>
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">4.1. The User's Personal Data is committed to maximum confidentiality according to E-News's regulations and the provisions of law. The processing of each User's Personal Data is only carried out with the User's consent, unless otherwise provided by law.</p>
                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">4.2. E-News does not use, transfer, provide or share with any third party any User's Personal Data without the User's consent, unless otherwise provided by law.</p>
                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">4.3. E-News will comply with other personal data security principles according to current law.</p>
                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">4.4. E-News uses various information security technologies to protect the User's Personal Data from being accessed, used or shared unintentionally. However, no data can be 100% secure. Therefore, E-News is committed to maximum confidentiality of the User's Personal Data. Some unexpected consequences and damages that may occur include but are not limited to:</p>
