                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">4.5. Users should protect electronic devices during use; Users should lock, log out, or exit their accounts on E-News's website or application when not in use.</p>
                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">5. Types of personal data that E-News collects and processes</p>
