                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">7.2. E-News commits to sharing or jointly processing personal data only when necessary to carry out the Processing Purposes stated in this Policy or as prescribed by law. Organizations and individuals receiving personal data of Users must comply with the provisions of this Policy and relevant provisions of law on personal data protection.</p>
