                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">11. Processing personal data with foreign elements</p>
                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">11.1. In order to carry out the purpose of processing personal data in this Policy, E-News may have to provide/share the User's personal data to E-News's related third parties and these third parties may be in Vietnam or any other location outside of Vietnam.</p>
                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">11.2. When providing/sharing personal data abroad, E-News will require the recipient to ensure that the User's personal data transferred to them will be confidential and secure. E-News ensures compliance with legal and regulatory obligations regarding the transfer of User personal data.</p>
                <hr style="border: solid 1px black; max-width: 300px">
                <p class="body-content" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px">11.3 Users in the European Union (EU): User personal data may be accessed, transferred and/or stored outside the European Economic Area (EEA), including to countries that may have a lower level of data protection under EU data protection laws. E-News must comply with specific rules when transferring Personal Data from within the EEA to outside the EEA. In such cases, E-News will use appropriate safeguards to protect any Personal Data transferred.</p>
